high_descs: turn left, walk towards TV, turn right, walk forward to black table with trophy on it
pick up the trophy that is on the table
hold the trophy up to the lamp that is on the right

high_descs: Turn to the left, and then to the right again to locate the black table.
Pick up the statue on the right side of the table.
Hold the statue and look to the right.
Continue holding the statue and turn the light on.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a statue and turn on a lamp.

high_descs: Turn to your left, walk forward, hang a right at the ottoman and walk up to the black table to the right of the piano.
Pick up the trophy that is on the right side of the table.
Hold the trophy up in the air.
Turn on the lamp that is to the right of where you are standing.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a trophy using the light of a lamp.
